{ Misc

  `V$TEMPSEG_USAGE` is a synonym that points to `V_$SORT_USAGE` (which is the view that the synonym `V$SORT_USAGE` points to):
code {
select * from dba_synonyms where synonym_name = 'V$TEMPSEG_USAGE';
code }

}

